<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Although spaces are not a valid input format for urls browsers often allow them because they are easy to detect and translit.</p>

<p>Zend_Uri should as part of a "lightweight" approach allow to validate such urls and make this option available to Zend Http Client which suffers from this unability.</p>

